name: Skyfall 64
description:
GMTK Game Jam 2021 submission

Stand by for Skyfall. Try to get the maximum score with your gang of skydivers by grabbing onto everyone and staying in the optimum zone. There is only one active skydiver at a time 

Controls for the active skydiver:
W, A, S, D - Move 

E, Q - Rotate 

K - Grab onto highlighted skydiver

L - Let go of previous skydiver

Space - Lock in current formation

Press Esc at any time to quit
